The system requires following sofware and libraries. 
python. Version 3.11 64bit

# Python Libraries
numpy. Version 1.24.2
pandas. Version 1.5.3
scipy. Version 1.10.1
statsmodels. Version 0.13.5
yfinance. Version 0.2.14
cvxpy. Version 1.3.1
pgmpy. Version 0.1.21

# Install using pip install numpy pandas scipy cvxpy statsmodels yfinance pgmpy
